.name
KCommodity
.type
OS utility
.short
Full featured commodity
.description
Multifunctional commodity for OS 2.0.  Includes window-
activator, time-display in several modes and formats, alarm
function, KeyStroke-Clicker, time to environment, Window/
Screen cycling, LeftyMouse, ESC-Key can close Windows,
Revision Control System, telefone bill calculator, Screen-
/Mouse-Blanker, Mapping of german "Umlauts", PopUp Shell,
AppIcon support, LeftyMouse, user definable HotKeys.  Fully
controllable via ARexx-Port.  All settings can be customized
and saved to disk using an "User Interface Style Guide"
compliant GUI.
